{"tid":533764,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"肥絲和廚子　都是連登kai子 羅曼史　開場於　飲食台爭議","createTime":"2018-01-19T06:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T06:45:49.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dff53549e5e54dd0067d627a48368a8b48689d25","tid":533764,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"肥絲和廚子　都是連登kai子<br />\n肥絲　原最愛連登裡捉人錯字<br />\n廚子　只喜愛發癲<br />\n偏偏他倆　早見晚見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每日著住同樣　純白襯衣</span><br />\n羅曼史　開場於　飲食台爭議<br />\n不過二人　好撚放肆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">能成為密友　大概總帶著愛<br />\n但做對好兄弟　又如此相愛　旁人會說不該<br />\n忘形時搭膊　自有一面退開<br />\n暗裡很享受　卻怕講出來<br />\n兩眼即使　移開轉開<br />\n心裡面也知　這是愛<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n劣改<br />\n有冇人改哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231f3680b7edd29452ef9ce36dd486b7acc710d8","tid":533764,"uid":8336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:39:37.000Z","msg":"我知你邊間教會架.jpg"},{"pid":"387c4c54208b3b6cba993dd97dc2ffe8fcb7fbc5","tid":533764,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"郭富城 弱？"},{"pid":"13784420d51e60274fbb477c9bcffeab8ee2264d","tid":533764,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387c4c54208b3b6cba993dd97dc2ffe8fcb7fbc5","tid":533764,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"郭富城 弱？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0667ced845c15bb4bd1039b7d97db9c8b4311c47","tid":533764,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"邊間教會?"}]}